@startuml
title PQR Hybrid Lakehouse - Secuencia Operativa Local (Boot + Verificacion)
skinparam shadowing false

actor Dev as "Usuario/Dev"
participant Compose as "docker compose"
participant PG as "postgres"
participant DaskS as "dask-scheduler"
participant DaskW as "dask-worker"
participant Prefect as "prefect-server"
participant Supa as "supabase overlay\n(kong/auth/rest/meta/studio)"
participant Obs as "prometheus/grafana"
participant Browser as "Navegador"

Dev -> Compose : up -d --build --remove-orphans
Compose -> PG : iniciar + init scripts SQL
PG --> Compose : healthy

Compose -> DaskS : iniciar scheduler
DaskS --> Compose : healthy
Compose -> DaskW : iniciar workers\n(depends_on scheduler healthy)

Compose -> Prefect : iniciar server (4200)
Prefect --> Compose : healthy

Compose -> Supa : iniciar kong/auth/rest/meta/studio
Supa --> Compose : running/healthy*

Compose -> Obs : iniciar prometheus + grafana
Obs --> Compose : running

Dev -> Compose : ps
Compose --> Dev : todos Up + healthy clave

Dev -> Browser : abrir UIs
Browser -> Prefect : http://localhost:4200
Prefect --> Browser : 200
Browser -> Supa : http://localhost:3002
Supa --> Browser : 307/200 (normal)
Browser -> DaskS : http://localhost:8787
DaskS --> Browser : 200
Browser -> Obs : http://localhost:3001
Obs --> Browser : 200

Dev -> Compose : run pipelines (Prefect/Dask)
DaskW -> PG : carga bronze/silver/gold + meta

note right of Supa
Studio puede quedar "unhealthy" intermitente
si responde en browser (307/200), operativo.
end note

@enduml
